<TEXT>
Cape apples are the best buys this week with Golden Delicious, Granny Smith,
Starkrimson and Starking varieties all priced at 40-50p a lb (40-60p).
Pineapples at 90p-Pounds 1.50p each (90p-Pounds 1.50). The first English
asparagus has made an appearance this week and is priced at Pounds 1.50-1.80
a lb. English Onions at 20-25p a lb (20-25p), flat mushrooms at 50-60p a
1/2 lb (50-60p). Homegrown and Dutch cucumbers are increasing in supply and
are available at 50-70p each (50-70p). Celery at 55-60p a head (55-60p),
Spring Onions at 30-35p a bunch (30-35p). (NB Last weeks prices shown in
brackets).
