liquidation of a company to which it had sold 51 estate agency offices.
Mr Peter Hughes, a partner in Corbould Rigby &amp; Co, acting for two of the
landlords and co-ordinating investigations for a further 10, said yesterday
the group had been deterred by the likely cost of High Court action against
Northern Rock, the 11th largest building society.
